{"tid":2075163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：將設特別扣留中心 國安法疑犯可被無限期扣留","createTime":"2020-06-22T15:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T16:04:09.000Z","uid":7542,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"765c969b0daa6340d992aaa5e23ab8d29a036b6e","tid":2075163,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"《南華早報》引述消息指，港區国安法的疑犯有機會被送至特別扣留中心，不設扣留時限。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士形容特別扣留中心的運作類似港英年代的摩星嶺白屋，但未有透露扣留中心的大小、位置和數目，亦未知扣留中心歸誰管轄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3090131/national-security-law-hong-kong-suspects-may-be-held\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Flaw-and-crime%2Farticle%2F3090131%2Fnational-security-law-hong-kong-suspects-may-be-held&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=092e58bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3090131/national-security-law-hong-kong-suspects-may-be-held</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>同東德 100% match <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF-SKS89xxRg&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=9ad5ec64\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg</a>"},{"pid":"60d601057e10955234ff4b6ab03a5db89d972641","tid":2075163,"uid":56624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"就係新屋嶺隔離個缸瓦甫行動基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f553a3246db2ef07436fa21ae8001c61295b431","tid":2075163,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"第一個捉史墨客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" c